{
  "texts": [
    "It also lays the foundation for researchers to quickly find previous experiments of interest to them.",
    "Situations may arise where obtaining precise coordinates for certain locations becomes a complex endeavor.",
    "These challenges can stem from various factors, including governmental restrictions imposed in specific countries or regions, intellectual property protection, or concerns related to data privacy and property rights.",
    "These issues are particularly prominent in datasets associated with potentially sensitive subjects, such as high levels of pathogens or antibiotic resistance genes (Serwecińska, 2020).",
    "In some cases, private landowners may be unwilling to disclose the exact locations of their facilities."
  ]
}